{"name": "J.M. Barrie\n    ", "description": "Sir James Matthew Barrie, 1st Baronet, OM (9 May 1860 \u2013 19 June 1937) was a Scottish author and dramatist, best remembered today as the creator of Peter Pan.The child of a family of small-town weavers, he was educated in Scotland", "born": "May 09, 1860 in Kirriemuir, Angus, Scotland, The United Kingdom"}
